Was it okay?

25
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,360
Your work

26
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,440
has always been perfect!

27
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,360
Then I'm leaving.

28
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:25,400
