92
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,360
I heard they call you that

93
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,620
at the security check.

94
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:48,960
Yes.

95
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,530
I'm Zhousheng Chen.

96
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,440
Here's the thing.

97
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,560
I've seen your name

98
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,250
